|Entry=Frame Relation Type
|Description=In the Wiki, frames (both cogs and frames) are listed along with information that contextualizes and relates the frame to other frames, either more generic frames from which it inherits or related frames which it commonly uses or is co-activated with. For instance, in the entry for the frame Motor_control, the related frame Action is listed. ''The current possible relation types are:'' 1. makes use of, 2. is a subcase/specific case/subframe of, and 3. is somehow related to.
|Utility=Wiki
|Entered by=Elise, 
