{{Glossary
|Entry=Role
|Other Aliases=Frame role; Semantic roles; Frame role; Frame element
|Description=Frames, both cogs and frames, are given roles (as many as are needed to understand the frame inferences, and as detailed as need be in terms of naming). When frames appear in a metaphor mapping, the same roles as were listed for that frame in its frame form entry appear in the metaphor mapping. Generally, the roles are assigned names that make them maximally relevant to and reflective of the frame they are roles of, and maximally distinct from the more generic frame from which they inherit.
|Entered by=Elise, 
}}

